META
    ics_scan_id `selinux_status_test`
    control_framework `RHEL_9_STIG`
    control `SV-257780r925324_rule`
    platform `RHEL_9`
    criticality `high`
    tags `selinux, mandatory_access_control, security`
META_END

DEF
VAR enforcing_mode string `Enforcing`

OBJECT selinux_system
    check_type `enforcement`
    type `selinux`
OBJECT_END

STATE enforcing_required
    mode string = VAR enforcing_mode
    enforcing boolean = true
STATE_END

CRI AND
    CTN selinux_status
        TEST all all
        STATE_REF enforcing_required
        OBJECT_REF selinux_system
    CTN_END
CRI_END
DEF_END